  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227960/extras/fcaa238a90411bda88433ba8cc08dbbe.avif?t=1720814860\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><br><i>Active Opposition is a story-based game where we play the actions of Adam and his brother to rise in the criminal world.</i><br><br><br>STORY<br><br><i>An intelligence agent has been kidnapped. Since the operation is not official, the state cannot intervene in the situation. The most suitable name for this job is Adam, a newcomer to the city.<br>Adam strives to rise in the criminal underworld, he will find himself in the midst of schemes he never understood and he will need his brother’s help to face the hurdles</i><br><br><br>İSTANBUL<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227960/extras/dffff950021aede4821dd8cc0ee75c9a.avif?t=1720814860\" width=600 height=250 /></span><br><br><i>You'll witness historical landmarks on a map inspired by Istanbul, and you'll shake the stones from their places in this elder city.</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227960/extras/b919c3d565619263472ba6b528d498f9.avif?t=1720814860\" width=600 height=250 /></span><br><br><br>ADAM<br>Ruthlessly eliminating his enemies,Adam does not consider the consequences of his actions<br><br><br><i>Take cover and survive the fight. If you don't spend your bullets carefully, you may get into trouble.</i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227960/extras/cafc70af043805b7b62224e238db4f94.avif?t=1720814860\" width=600 height=250 /></span><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227960/extras/71e19f7dc4a1fd06760f7fd5c9eec547.avif?t=1720814860\" width=600 height=250 /></span><br><br><br>METO<br>Even though he wants to solve problems with his intelligence,events will quickly get out of his control<br><br><br><i>Climb and peek to get one step ahead of events</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227960/extras/4028ff196f7970226514bc8b162b74bc.avif?t=1720814860\" width=600 height=250 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227960/extras/fa386f9aa901d485692d685c7e23d80b.avif?t=1720814860\" width=600 height=250 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227960/extras/fcaa238a90411bda88433ba8cc08dbbe.avif?t=1720814860\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><br><i>Active Opposition is a story-based game where we play the actions of Adam and his brother to rise in the criminal world.</i><br><br><br>STORY<br><br><i>An intelligence agent has been kidnapped. Since the operation is not official, the state cannot intervene in the situation. The most suitable name for this job is Adam, a newcomer to the city.<br>Adam strives to rise in the criminal underworld, he will find himself in the midst of schemes he never understood and he will need his brother’s help to face the hurdles</i><br><br><br>İSTANBUL<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227960/extras/dffff950021aede4821dd8cc0ee75c9a.avif?t=1720814860\" width=600 height=250 /></span><br><br><i>You'll witness historical landmarks on a map inspired by Istanbul, and you'll shake the stones from their places in this elder city.</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227960/extras/b919c3d565619263472ba6b528d498f9.avif?t=1720814860\" width=600 height=250 /></span><br><br><br>ADAM<br>Ruthlessly eliminating his enemies,Adam does not consider the consequences of his actions<br><br><br><i>Take cover and survive the fight. If you don't spend your bullets carefully, you may get into trouble.</i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227960/extras/cafc70af043805b7b62224e238db4f94.avif?t=1720814860\" width=600 height=250 /></span><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227960/extras/71e19f7dc4a1fd06760f7fd5c9eec547.avif?t=1720814860\" width=600 height=250 /></span><br><br><br>METO<br>Even though he wants to solve problems with his intelligence,events will quickly get out of his control<br><br><br><i>Climb and peek to get one step ahead of events</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227960/extras/4028ff196f7970226514bc8b162b74bc.avif?t=1720814860\" width=600 height=250 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227960/extras/fa386f9aa901d485692d685c7e23d80b.avif?t=1720814860\" width=600 height=250 /></span>",
